  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/a1a490aafb53472026d89f98705300b5.poster.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/a1a490aafb53472026d89f98705300b5.webm?t=1680103295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/a1a490aafb53472026d89f98705300b5.mp4?t=1680103295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/ffccc7c8f83b40631e3f72b6b043f2c0.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 /></span><br>Turn, grind, and drive your way to the top. Radical Road is an easy to learn but hard to master single button arcade game!<br>The objective is to go as far as you can on an infinitely procedurally generated road!<br>Along the way you will have to turn and grind with the correct timing to avoid bailing out!<br>The further you go the faster the car goes and the more points you rack up!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/37ca6aa5daa899cd78ac4a4c6887b070.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 /></span><br>The further you go the more coins you will collect!<br>You can then use said coins to unlock a variety of <strong>EPIC</strong> skins for your vehicle<br>so you can ride in style. All the skins you unlock feature distinct visual effects and more!<br>Besides coins you have 15 Achievements to attain and a sprinkel of some <i>Cool Secrets</i> to find.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/9809a20bed7fef71ca5cf01e0012d0d2.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 /></span><br>Compete with your friends or take on the world on the global leaderboard, see if you have what it takes to be the <strong>MOST RADICALLEST</strong> roader around!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/79297b75f1e2a1627966bd3e93edbcd1.poster.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/79297b75f1e2a1627966bd3e93edbcd1.webm?t=1680103295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/79297b75f1e2a1627966bd3e93edbcd1.mp4?t=1680103295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/a1a490aafb53472026d89f98705300b5.poster.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/a1a490aafb53472026d89f98705300b5.webm?t=1680103295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/a1a490aafb53472026d89f98705300b5.mp4?t=1680103295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/ffccc7c8f83b40631e3f72b6b043f2c0.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 /></span><br>Turn, grind, and drive your way to the top. Radical Road is an easy to learn but hard to master single button arcade game!<br>The objective is to go as far as you can on an infinitely procedurally generated road!<br>Along the way you will have to turn and grind with the correct timing to avoid bailing out!<br>The further you go the faster the car goes and the more points you rack up!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/37ca6aa5daa899cd78ac4a4c6887b070.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 /></span><br>The further you go the more coins you will collect!<br>You can then use said coins to unlock a variety of <strong>EPIC</strong> skins for your vehicle<br>so you can ride in style. All the skins you unlock feature distinct visual effects and more!<br>Besides coins you have 15 Achievements to attain and a sprinkel of some <i>Cool Secrets</i> to find.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/9809a20bed7fef71ca5cf01e0012d0d2.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 /></span><br>Compete with your friends or take on the world on the global leaderboard, see if you have what it takes to be the <strong>MOST RADICALLEST</strong> roader around!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/79297b75f1e2a1627966bd3e93edbcd1.poster.avif?t=1680103295\" width=584 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/79297b75f1e2a1627966bd3e93edbcd1.webm?t=1680103295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310860/extras/79297b75f1e2a1627966bd3e93edbcd1.mp4?t=1680103295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
